Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:16.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以往不同 Feel So Good
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:20.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂人情世故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel So Good
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:31.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人情世故我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:36.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:45.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel So Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:57.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月亮的沙漠上与你共舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:11.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别输给兔子 高高蹦起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:15.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,550)}飞起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:12.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬头望去 星星过于耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:17.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以静静地闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:28.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信 独自瑟瑟发抖的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:35.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我就在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:39.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 手拉起手 用力握住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我们一直都这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:47.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着希望 成为眩光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:51.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样的“现在”都能跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:58.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看到吗 那美丽无比的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:05.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后的我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.79,0:23:12.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成声地 连珠般地泪滴 也..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:19.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会渐渐风干
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:28.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出一个 又一个的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:33.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬上夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,350)}{\pos(325,590)}#05  有所欠缺的日日夜夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:24:04.74,optitle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(927,550)}#06 在脑袋里萦绕的种种..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:06.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿国际机场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德克萨斯州
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与日本的时差大约15小时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 请问出口在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚到美国的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日人正准备出门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而命运也正要随之转动..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我为什么能免费去参观NASA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我是日日人的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NASA有一个叫“家庭支援计划”的企划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇航员们结束任务 平安回到地球之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NASA会帮忙关照组员们的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减轻宇航员们的忧虑情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让他们能更进一步的集中于任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在能不能进入第二阶段测试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是个未知数的这个状态下去见日日人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在有些不情愿..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我无法战胜来自NASA的召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NASA~在呼唤我~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿 太阳公园..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿波？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一个字就变成阿呆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明好名字多了去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然叫什么阿波..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上可什么好吃的都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追定我了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要着陆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现外星人！发现外星人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥是我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找别人去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有什么味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只叫阿波的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不过是租的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.21,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维护模块 CES-51计划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 差点忘了..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴手礼伴手礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有说过不需要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可老妈吵着要我带来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:17.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz353}{\move(733,240,1054,240,0,8740)}可做零食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:17.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz353}{\move(733,280,1054,280,0,8740)}可做夜宵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:17.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz37}{\move(448,300,778,300,0,8740)}难以想象的好味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:17.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(741,558,1080,558,0,8740)}肉包子 五个入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:17.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(811,609,1160,609,0,8740)}使用极品猪肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微波炉加热的肉包子还有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咸味海苔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柿P牌脆米饼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有差两天就要过期的韩国泡菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“去美国的话因为时差赏味期也会延长啦”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一样都槽点十足还真有老妈的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是把自己不要的东西丢给你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为不会这么老梗..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是“阿波罗”的“阿波”啊- -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一个“罗”根本用不着省略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你从以前开始就有这种懒得管细节的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说窗帘漏钩一节也不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯少点一盏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海报掉了一角
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明注意到了却不去补正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“有点想在屋子里放个植物啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“但是浇水又好烦啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一番烦恼之后..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有了这个仙人掌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且再仔细一看 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标签撕到一半又放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院子里应该也有些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往的注意细节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己享受起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了啊 这个院子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这什么啊我有点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以前一起在DVD里看过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的人就是在这样的院子里这么做..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:57.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：原著漫画中给出，这是电影《阿波罗13》中汤姆·汉克斯做出的手势。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个有什么涵义吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不知道有没有什么涵义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直径3467公里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离地球距离38万4千公里..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算罗列出这些天文数字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果从我们这看出去 用一只大拇指就遮住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到那种一般人绝对触及不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而自己的弟弟马上就要去了..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉非常地..不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六哥也要去那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得还真轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去在暑假的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经骑脚踏车跑去京都的奶奶家吧 两人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候花了几天来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天..四天？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去京都用了三天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过去月球用火箭也是三天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一想就已经不是那么遥不可及的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是开始觉得去那里并非难事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我趁这个机会好好跟你说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我和你啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在立场上..在各种情况上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..差太多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到月球的距离也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前可是不一样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不会明白的吧 日日人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我到哪里都只会被称为南波日日人的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？难道你是南波日日人的亲戚之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都传开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您居然是那个南波日日人宇航员的哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 南波君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次能不能帮我问日日人要一个签名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一个人肯叫我南波六太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在和以前有所区别的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是小六哥..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像以前那样充满干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 那个日日人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一直觉得..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很..无聊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..就早点跟我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}脑子里少拧颗螺丝这个比喻对于日日人还真是"Just fit"啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里少了个at
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀子的前面少了个“k”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,k？为什么是k？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不发音 但就是有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么嘛 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为一个k就烦起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我看你这一整个人就少了点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也少了一撇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“麦克在等待肯恩”才是正解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然成了麦克在等“侍”肯恩..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还武士呢？ 麦克要砍肯恩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：侍=日本武士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克kill肯恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 只不过有点像而已别耍宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有莎朗阿姨教英文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种分数的话 阿姨会哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的弟弟以前是个对学习一窍不通的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 所有的学习都是我来教他的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以日日人在中学里成绩嗖嗖往上窜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是我的教学有方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看来并不是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有一天 日日人的成绩变得比我更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去约翰逊太空中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完早餐就来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 故意用英文写
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在测试我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且..约翰逊的“h”漏写了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:13:00.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(525,660)}Johnson
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是训练的教范啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双面复印还有这么多页数还真是恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙..把这个全读了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿波？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你是六太？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 六太六太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什..什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的热狗也没有特别好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过阿波非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 一直是史密斯夫妇俩带着阿波散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日人的左邻右舍都有养狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家轮流着来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日日人训练的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉拙弟日日人一直在麻烦你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是喜欢才干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说麻烦 不如说日日人一直在把精神带给我们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用关于宇宙的故事或者和你之间的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们听了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心是不是有正确地传达到..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得他缺点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最适合形容日日人的话是..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士男孩 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子里少拧颗螺丝..是也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球的重力也换好玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 要是没有水的话就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？小六哥还没有来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在..在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是看不懂我的留言之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 欢迎回家 日日人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你做了晚餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙人命名为“快过期的泡菜套餐”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说料理的实力我在你之上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山手线的全部站名也是我能更快背出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有J联盟的2025年份选手人名录我也全部背熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从刚才开始就在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么..只是说我也是充满干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是指这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上逞强有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么用模仿秀来决胜负吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要来颗足球我马上就会被人说是RamosRuy哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:51.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RamosRuy：ラモス瑠偉，是日本籍的巴西球员，特征为乱蓬头。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你就吃你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去睡一会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六哥 明天来参观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底千里迢迢来这里干什么来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我明白..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那简直就是小学四年级..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用小四的我去挑战有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋里少一颗螺丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:18:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在日本人们就是这么称呼日日人这样少根筋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 少点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论谁都不是完好无缺的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六太 我跟你真是一见如故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是从日日人那里听了你的故事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某一天我问了日日人这么个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六太现在在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他这么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六哥现在应该在日本做着成为宇航员的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论问他多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六太在准备中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六太在准备中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六太在准备中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于认定了你会来的日日人来说..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些孤身奋进的日日夜夜会不会让他觉得有所欠缺呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓哥哥..不走在弟弟前面怎么行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓哥哥..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了啦 日日人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至日日人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没有去是因为起得太晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我也会去NASA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且会起得比你早！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南波六太和沢木学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说必须刷掉其中一位的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会毫不犹豫地刷掉南波
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到休斯顿的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于去了圣地约翰逊宇航中心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是每个人都是“日日人”“日日人”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底是多有人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 哥哥是令我自豪的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而期间从日本传来了最差劲的噩耗
